reviewText: Alright Movie IF Your A Kendrick Lamar Fan
I am a K-Dot fan so this belongs in my collection. It is poor quality, particularly the sound, but you get to know Kendrick a little more by watching.

I saw everything on youtube prior to this dvd. I guess its cool to actually have on dvd but I could have also went without. PRO: Its a cool moment on there where its just him going through the motions...if you are a major fan it will be "cool" but not worth the money lol. Again..just head to Youtube.

to be honest i haven't watched all of this.
no time.
what i did watch was informative.
kendrick is an artist for the future.
but he's so good NOW that it's ridiculous.

highly recommended.
